Here (and many other places in tests) I put the lambda on the end of line to have:

```dart
testWidgets('xxxx', (WidgetTester tester) async {
  xxxxxx
  xxxxxx
  xxxxxx
});
```

instead of:

```dart
testWidgets('xxxx',
  (WidgetTester tester) async {
    xxxxxx
    xxxxxx
    xxxxxx
  });
```

or:

```dart
testWidgets(
  'xxxx',
  (WidgetTester tester) async {
    xxxxxx
    xxxxxx
    xxxxxx
  },
);
```

This reduces the number of lines changed by this PR.

